    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatjone eius millesimo octuagesimo primo,
                        temporibus domni <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/265"
                            >Gregorii</persName> pape cum sede [a]nno octavo, regnante <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77">Henrico</persName> quondam Henritj
                        impera[tori]s filio, die viesimo primo mensis novembris, ind(itjo)n(e)
                        quarta, [in <rs key="#Fundi">fun]do</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fundi"><placeName key="#Fundi"
                            >Salecto</placeName></geogName>. Petivi a vobis in Dei nomine <persName
                            key="#Monks"><name ref="Wido Pomposianus">Wido</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Maurizo Pomposianus"
                            >Mauritjus</name></persName> hone[sti <rs key="#Monks">m]onachi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in
                                <placeName ref="#places/4179">Ponposea</placeName></orgName>, cum
                        consensu domni <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1599"
                            >Geronimi</persName> nostri <rs key="#Abbots">abatis</rs> et cum
                        consensu monachorum eiusdem monasterii, michi presenti in Christi nomine
                        <persName
                            ><name ref="Fuscardus">Fuscardo</name></persName> petitor pro me et 
                        pro iugale mea silicet <persName
                            ><name ref="Inga">Inga</name></persName> seu filiis et
                        nepotibus nostris sub dominium et potestatem <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs> <persName
                            key="#Priests"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> fratris tui,
                                per <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfiteuticario iure</rs> 
                                concessistis et largistis michi rem iuris predicti
                        monasterii vestri, idest omnes res et pertinentjas vestras quas usque modo
                        posedit <persName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            ><name ref="Petrus Sturianus">Petrus Sturianus</name></persName> 
                                iure predicto monasterio que sunt posite in fundo
                        <geogName key="#Fundi" ref="#estates/3949"><placeName key="#Fundi">Meriaule</placeName></geogName>, 
                                cum ingresso et regresso suo et cum omnibus suis pertinentjis,
                        sitas <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs> 
                                <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2424"><placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/3513">Faventino</placeName></geogName> 
                                acto Corneliensis, <rs key="#Plebs">plebe</rs> 
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3627">Sancti Iohannis in
                        Libba</orgName>, <rs key="#Confinia">interraffines</rs> eius hoc est: ab uno latere detinet eres quondam
                        <persName key="#Confinia"
                            ><name ref="Rusticus de Comperto">Rustici de Comperto</name></persName>, 
                        ab alio latere Romaldus filius quondam Alberti
                        iudicis, a tertjo latere | Uuido presbiteri Ursonis, a quarto latere vos
                        predicti ordinatoris. Et insuper addi|distis michi una petjola terre que est
                        posita in fundo Maserie, | cum ingresso et regresso suo et cum omnibus suis
                        pertinentjis, con|stituta vero in predicto territorio et in predicta plebe,
                        | interraffines eius idest: ab uno latere detinet Romaldus, ab alio latere
                        Ugo | Gerardi filius, a tertjo iuris monasterii Sancti Adalberti, a quarto
                        latere via | percurente. Hec omnia abendas, tenendas, defensandas et in
                        omnibus | meliorandas, pensionis nomine singulis quibusque anni omni martji
                        mense infra ind(itjo)n(e) denariis monete Venetje duodetjm tantum, pensio ut
                        dic|tum est persolvatur. Call(tjarii) | nomine, idest librum unum pro
                        denariis monete | Venetje libras tres. Si quis vero partis nostre contra
                        hanc aparam | henfiteosin ire temtaverimus ante perfinitum tempus sicut(a)
                        superius | legitur det pars partis fidem servantis, ante omne litis
                        i|nitjum(b) aut interpell(atjonem), pene nomine, | auri untjas duas et post
                        penam | solutam hec appara henfiteosin maneat ratam. Wido de Faven(tina) |
                        patria Dei misericordia tabellio scribendum rogavi, sub die et mense et
                        ind(itjo)n(e) | suprascripta quarta. Signum + manus predicti Fuscardi in ac
                        appara a me facta subscripsi.</ab>
